@page "/projects"

<PageTitle>项目 - Zero72 博客</PageTitle>

<main class="main-content page">
    <header class="page-header">
        <span class="eyebrow">Selected work</span>
        <h1>项目与实验</h1>
        <p>围绕博客、开发效率和真实业务问题构建的产品与工具。</p>
    </header>

    <section>
        <div class="cards">
            <article class="card">
                <span class="project-label">Web · 2026</span>
                <h2>Zero72 博客</h2>
                <p>基于 Blazor WebAssembly、.NET Web API、PostgreSQL 和 Docker 的个人博客项目。</p>
                <div class="card-links">
                    <a class="button secondary small" href="/blog">文章</a>
                    <a class="button secondary small" href="https://github.com/mmgdh" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">源码</a>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="card">
                <span class="project-label">Android · 2026</span>
                <h2>Zero72 移动助手</h2>
                <p>使用 .NET MAUI Blazor 构建，随时记录阅读进度、临时感悟并安全同步到博客。</p>
                <div class="card-links">
                    <a class="button secondary small" href="/notes">查看思考</a>
                    <a class="button secondary small" href="https://github.com/mmgdh" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">源码</a>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>
